---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Horizon Dubai Property — Your Trusted Dubai Real Estate Partner" description="Meet the Horizon Dubai team. AI-powered property matching, verified listings, Golden Visa assistance. Marina is your personal consultant in Dubai.">

  <section class="hero-gradient py-32 lg:py-40">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="gradient-line mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white">About Horizon Dubai</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/60 text-lg">AI-powered property matching meets local expertise</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Horizon Dubai Property is part of the Horizon Property AI platform — a technology-driven real estate agency that uses artificial intelligence to find, verify, and match properties for international investors.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Founded by Aleksandr Doronin (CEO, Blockchain Industrial Alliance), Horizon combines cutting-edge AI technology with on-the-ground expertise. Our AI monitors thousands of listings across Dubai's real estate market, while our human team handles viewings, negotiations, and paperwork.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-10">We also operate <a href="https://horizonpropertyai.com" class="text-gold hover:text-gold-dark underline">Horizon Bali Property</a>, serving the Bali market with the same AI-powered approach.</p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Team</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-sand-light rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Aleksandr Doronin</h3>
          <p class="text-gold text-sm font-medium mb-3">CEO & Founder</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Technology entrepreneur, CEO of Blockchain Industrial Alliance. Drives the AI and platform technology behind Horizon's property matching system.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-sand-light rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Marina</h3>
          <p class="text-gold text-sm font-medium mb-3">Property Consultant — Dubai</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Dubai-based property consultant. Handles viewings, negotiations, DLD registration, and Golden Visa applications. Available in English, Russian, and Arabic.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex gap-3">
            <a href="https://wa.me/971528486680" class="text-sm text-gold hover:text-gold-dark">WhatsApp</a>
            <a href="https://t.me/Dubaimarina1202" class="text-sm text-gold hover:text-gold-dark">Telegram</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Horizon?</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"><span class="text-lg">🤖</span></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">AI-Powered Discovery</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Our AI scans the market 24/7, finding properties that match your criteria before they get snapped up.</p></div></div>
        <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"><span class="text-lg">✅</span></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Verified Listings</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Every listing is verified through RERA, DLD records, and developer track records.</p></div></div>
        <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"><span class="text-lg">🛂</span></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Golden Visa Support</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">End-to-end assistance finding eligible properties and processing your 10-year visa.</p></div></div>
        <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"><span class="text-lg">🌍</span></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">International Focus</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We specialize in helping international buyers navigate Dubai's market with confidence.</p></div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary inline-block">Contact Marina</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
